defaultHomeless Link
default (HL)
default is the national umbrella organisation for frontline homelessness charities in England. Currently we have more than 500 member organisations
default. As the collaborative hub for information and debate on homelessness, we seek to improve services for homeless peo
defaultple and to advocate for policy change. Through this work, we aim to end homelessness in England
default.
default&#xa0;
defaultWe are delighted to respond to this consultation
default which poses critical questions for the future funding and sustainability of support costs in housing
default. Most of
default our response will cover areas specific to single homelessness although at points we address wider issues.
