default7) The impact of these cumulative resource reductions is clearly being felt on the frontline
default, with services focused on employment, substance misuse and resettlement all been reduced. Nearly half of homelessness services are doing less work with complex needs clients, who are amongst the most vulnerable and marginalised citizens
